  <Name>Goblin Treasure Room</Name>
  <ShortDescription>This small room is where the goblins place their treasure.</ShortDescription>
  <LongDescription>Goblins search for treasure by raiding farming villages at night, and by
killing unsuspecting adventurers who walk into their lair.  Unfortunately,
the goblins' idea of treasure does not exactly coincide with the average
adventurer's idea.  The goblins tend to steal those things that amaze and
confuse them, without regard to precious metal content.  Still, the goblins
are bound to have something worth taking.</LongDescription>
  
